latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Routine. Is. Coming. What healthy lifestyle hacks are you bringing with you into fall?

We’ll go first: Make healthy the easy choice and keep your fridge fully stocked with simple, whole foods that you can grab whenever you need them. Oh look… we just made it 𝘦𝘹𝘵𝘳𝘢 easy for you 😉.
We're the cherry on top of your jam-packed day (and we’re honored to come along for the ride).
From hangry to happy in 0.5 seconds. We’re ready.

Hey you, let's wake up together. 

We soak our oats for hours so you can devour them in minutes, meaning you can savor more of your mornings, evenings, and everything in between.

CALLING ALL RUNNERS. 

“Consistent training requires the right balance of fuel”. - Drew Hunter, Professional Runner. 

We are so proud to have partnered with our friend @drewhunter00 , and we can’t wait to share some exciting projects we have in store for you 👀. 

Get your 👟’s ready.

MUSH is now available at Kroger!!!!! This launch comes on the heels of our expansion at Costco which brings MUSH's total retail footprint to nearly 11,000 stores 🥳🎉!!! Every time we expand, we can effect positive change in America at monumental scale, one cup of MUSH at a time. We are committed to growing WITHOUT compromising the quality of our ingredients. 

Six years ago, MUSH was not in a single grocery store. So again we are reminded: Start, even if you don’t know how. Because it's better to do something imperfectly than nothing flawlessly.
Keep your eyes peeled for a big announcement…👀

We’re still in awe of the brand building work facilitated by our partners at @manual_sf. Thank you to everyone who helped us glow up ✨.

If you’d be interested in hearing more about our rebranding process, let us know in the comments! 

📸 by the incredible @marencaruso.

JUST DROPPED!!! Introducing Carrot Cake and the return of Peaches and Cream! Carrot Cake perfectly mixes almond milk, rolled oats, carrots, date, pineapple, and a dash of sea salt, cinnamon and nutmeg for that nostalgic spring flavor. And back by VERY popular demand, Peaches and Cream is a mouthwatering combination of coconut milk, rolled oats, peaches, apples and a hint of sea salt for an elegantly sweet flavor. Both are exquisitely mushy and beyond healthy. We are obsessed and you will be too, so do not miss these!

✔️No more than 8 simple ingredients
✔️Fantastic source of protein and fiber
✔️Dairy-free, Gluten-Free, and No Added Sugar

Both are available exclusively on our website and at Whole Foods Market nationwide!
FOUR DAYS until the launch of our limited release flavors!!! #NOFOMO
Meet the extremely successful business owner, influencer, mom, and MUSH Queen, @kait.davis . Listen to her inspirational health story, it will get you moving no matter what may be in your way.
CAN YOU FEEL THE HYPE? Newest MUSH flavor drops tomorrow. Don’t miss it.
